author: Alexandra Schonfeld
title: The Protests Against Stay-at-Home Orders Around the Country, in Photos
description: Protests were seen Sunday in 9 states nationwide opposing statewide lockdowns and stay at home orders enacted to help stop the spread of COVID-19. For over a week, protests have been popping up around the country as states continue to tighten restrictions.
